    <item>
      <title>捷豹路虎车主预计印度需求将在 6 月份复苏，关注美国关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/jlr-owner-sees-india-demand-revival-by-june-watching-us-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在纳伦德拉·莫迪领导的印度政府为中产阶级减税 115 亿美元后，捷豹路虎的印度所有者发现，6 月底，这个世界最大人口国家的消费需求正在复苏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/jlr-owner-sees-india-demand-revival-by-june-watching-us-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 04:25:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>关税豁免预期推动香港中国股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/chinese-stocks-in-hong-kong-jump-on-hopes-of-tariff-reprieve</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，美国政府将与北京举行会谈，引发市场对世界第二大经济体能够避免痛苦的关税上调的希望，香港中国股市随之飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/chinese-stocks-in-hong-kong-jump-on-hopes-of-tariff-reprieve</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 02:52:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
